data.description: Buyer financing fell through. Back on the market!! Here’s another chance to buy this Gorgeous Brick Front Single Family House on a Premium Corner lot at Pearsons Landings! SHOWS LIKE A MODEL!! Over 4,100 finished square feet. Beautiful new luxury vinyl floors throughout the house. Updated Kitchen features large Island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. Large Family room off of kitchen with a gas fireplace. Separate Formal Dining and Living Room. Laundry on the main level. Luxury master bedroom suit with updated master bath with soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. Bright and Open Fully Finished Walk out basement with a bonus room, a fully functional kitchen (2020), separate laundry room, and a full Bath (2020). Newer roof and fence (2016) and water heater and HVAC system (2015). Great location with easy access to I-95, shopping, Potomac Mills, Quantico and Ft. Belvoir. Unbelievable Value! Wont’t last long!
